<plot>A couple who are vacationing take a detour and end up in an old inn. The wife decides that she would like to stay there, and somehow a room that the innkeeper has kept close for over twenty years opens and draws the wife into it and chooses to stay in there. All of a sudden all sorts of weird things begin to happen. Like the wife has a change in attitude. And a ghost speaks to her from the mirror in the room, and tells of secrets that her parents have from her. And learns that she's there to fulfill an evil legacy.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?231677</url></doc>
